summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 36726, entitled, "An Ordinance appropriating money from the General Fund to aid in the improvement of Rainier Avenue, from Hudson Street to Forty-second Avenue South, in connection with the improvement of Juneau Street et al, by grading, under Ordinance No. 31239, creating Local Improvement District No. 2657," approved November 22, 1916.
